We challenged resident Bon Appétit supertaster Chris Morocco to recreate Ina Garten's lobster pot pie recipe in the Bon Appétit Test Kitchen. The catch? He'll have to identify what he's making with a blindfold over his eyes, letting each of his other senses guide the way. Will Chris be able to reproduce each step the Barefoot Contessa takes without seeing the final product?&#13;
